Organization Resource Management System

A website to help an organization manage its internal resources (rooms, equipment, vehicles).

Key Features

Admin dashboard
Add/manage resources (projectors, laptops, meeting rooms, vehicles, etc.)
Booking system with calendar view
Approvals workflow
Usage reports & analytics
Email/SMS notifications
Why resource management
Demonstrates database design
Shows CRUD operations
Involves authentication, scheduling, and UI/UX
Can be used by schools, offices, or NGOs